tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE audit_trail (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT NOT NULL,
  action VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE audit_logs (
    log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    action VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE user_access_logs (
    access_log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    request_type VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    request_details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE data_modification_logs (
    modification_log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    table_name VARCHAR(50),
    action VARCHAR(50),
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE system_logs (
    system_log_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    log_level VARCHAR(20),
    log_message TEXT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
)

CREATE TABLE data_access_logs (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  data_table VARCHAR(50),
  action VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE data_modification_logs (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  modified_by VARCHAR(50),
  data_table VARCHAR(50),
  action VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE privacy_settings_logs (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  setting VARCHAR(50),
  action VARCHAR(50),
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
